    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "AGENT'S NOTE: A record check was made by telephone by Mr. Brady with the Seattle",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "Field Office, FBI, for records on [REDACTED]. The check on Mr. Crisman",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "was negative. The Seattle FBI indices indicated that a Harold Dahl had been charged",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "with two incidents of illegal wearing of the uniform and one with theft of national",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "property. It could not be determined at the time whether Harold A. Dahl, the subject",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "in question, and Harold Dahl of the FBI indices, was one and the same.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "5. [REDACTED] had indicated to [REDACTED] et al, that he was a",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "former fighter pilot and held commission as Captain in the Air Reserve.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "AGENT'S NOTE: On 8 August 47, this officer checked the records of the 406th AAF",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
